description.en:
Bulldog Liquidity locker aims to fundamentally redefine liquidity locking practices and set a precedent for the entire cryptosphere. It will be a better, faster, and more optimized service than all existing competition. Doing your research is always recommended, and we hope to make it more accessible for the everyday investor by providing helpful information on every coin featured in the liquidity locker, as well as the locker itself.

Regarding how fees are distributed, 70% will be collected in a multi-signature donation wallet then donated to user elected charities. The 30% remaining fees will go towards further developing the projects, tokens, and locker – not a single cent gets pocketed.

BDOG token is the premium currency used to access the Liquidity Lockers more premium features such as Presale, Incremental Locks, Autolocking and Lock Splitting. In addition to that, we plan to integrate more platforms than the rest of our competitors on release. BDOG will act as a revolutionary new utility for the ERC-20 market and a cryptocharity to help give back to those in need, all while providing a top-of-the-line service to the entire cryptosphere.
